                                "type": "link",
                                "url": "https:\/\/feelingof.com\/episodes\/079\/",
                                "text": "Feeling of Computing by Ivan Reese and Jimmy Miller and sometimes others, episode 79 • The Computer is a Feeling by Tim Hwang and Omar Rizwan"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n\nThis paper… is not a paper. What is it, other than a paper? Name the medium!\n\nA relatively short list of points generally on the theme of… the Computer is a Feeling.\n\nAs Ivan wrote over on the Feeling of Computing website:\n\n"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_quote",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "This piece makes us question what the computer means in our lives, and how that may have changed over time. Light on specifics and arguably steeped in nostalgic yearning, its series of declarative statements come out more like broadly probing questions. Is the computer feeling possessed only by those who remember the time before the internet? Are computers even required? What does "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "feeling this feeling",
                                "style": {
                                    "italic": true
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " elicit one to do?"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\nYeah, I have no idea either."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],
